nanashi

nanashi started as a fork of tui-chan by Arthur Kurbidaev (tuqqu),
https://github.com/tuqqu/tui-chan, which is MIT licensed (Copyright (c) 2021
Arthur Kurbidaev). The three-pane layout and the groundwork that left room for
more than one imageboard both came from that project. Thanks to tuqqu for the
starting point.

nanashi isn't affiliated with 4chan, or with any other site it can talk to. It's
an independent client that uses public APIs. However you use it, stick to the
rules of whatever site you point it at.
